        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'Having brought down his final adversary with a resounding stomp, Spooner pivots around, only to behold a scattered landscape of machine parts. Rendered lifeless, each piece lies cleaved in perfect halves, a testament to the surgical precision of Haicma\\'s scythe.'}"
    },
    {
