        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Sword 4', 3: 'Hey, Sword 9, can you hold your horses and give me a break? These encryption methods are completely new to me. If it were anyone else, I bet they\\'d spend a good three days just trying to find a loophole in the firewall.', 4: '2'}"
